<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Margarethe Drahtschmied</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass sie oder ihr Bevollmächtigter wegen des Streits mit Hans Veierabend, Bürger zu Nürnberg, von Dienstag bis Samstag nach Lichtmess vor das Gericht zu Nürnberg kommen kann und gewährt ihr dazu Geleit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_217" id="108r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_217_r2l11">Margrethen <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Drotſmidin </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l14">von Jngolſtat / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_217_r2l12">von <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Rate </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l13">cʒü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l15"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> beuor / Margret Drotſmidin / Als vvir dir vormals </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l16">hie vor <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Gerichte cʒü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> des rechten geholffen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hanſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l18">Veyrabent <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> / vnd du 
<add><ab facs="#facs_217_r1l1">auf der </ab><ab facs="#facs_217_r1l2">ſchrannen </ab><ab facs="#facs_217_r1l3"><expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_217_r1l4">haſt vnd </ab></add> mainſt / daʒ du noch mer cʒü Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l20"> <expan>cʒüſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habſt / . Alſo / 
<del rend="strikethrough">wer ſecʒen </del> beſcheıden wir dir 
<add><ab facs="#facs_217_r2l17">gen <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> </ab></add> / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Ob du cʒü </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l21">tage cʒü <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> gen <expan>de<ex>m</ex>ſelben</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_217_line_1576593602346_5670">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan><gap reason="illegible"/></del></ab></add> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> es ſeÿ </del> auf den 
<add><ab facs="#facs_217_r2l19">nehſten </ab></add> Eritag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l22"><expan>Mitwoch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Pfincʒtag freÿtag <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> Samſtag nach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l23">tag cʒe Lıechtmeʒʒ nu ſchirſt / vnd auf welıchen <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag du </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l24">kümſt / <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dein ſcheimbot mit <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt / vnd das an vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l25">vorderſt / So <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir dir <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheimbot<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan> vollen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l26">gewalt von <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>obgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> Hanſen veyrabent <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnu<ex>er</ex></del> hie vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l27">des Reiches <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒoge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſlewnige<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l28">helffen / vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">du ſolt vnſer </del> dar cʒü ſolt du vnſer ſıcher geleitt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l29"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / cʒü vns beÿ vns vnd <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> vns <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l30"><expan>qu<ex>in</ex>ta</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Purific<ex>acionis</ex></expan> Marıe / . </ab>
<note place="bottomcentral"><ab facs="#facs_217_r2l31">Den brief hat man Jr <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> cʒü <expan>Eyſt<ex>et</ex></expan> am Samſtag vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l32"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen tag / Da bey was <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Dıckerman / vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>meıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab></note>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_217" id="108r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Margrethen, <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Drotsmidin von Ingolstat </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab>Von <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> rate czü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>.
                                <expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> bevor. Margret Drotsmidin, als wir dir
                        vormals hie vor <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> gerichte czü
                                <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> des rechten geholffen
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hansen Veyrabent, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, und du <add>auf der schrannen
                                    <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hast und</add> mainst, daz du
                        noch mer czü im <expan>czüsprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habst, also bescheiden
                        wir dir <add>gen <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan></add> tage czü
                            <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <app><note><q type="date">auf den <add>nehsten</add> eritag</q>03.02.1411</note></app>,
    <app><note><q type="date"><expan>mitwoch<ex>e</ex>n</expan></q>04.02.1411</note></app>, <app><note><q type="date">pfincztag</q>05.02.1411</note></app>, <app><note><q type="date">freytag</q>06.02.1411</note></app>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <app><note><q type="date">samstag nach
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen tag cze liechtmezz nu schirst</q>07.02.1411</note></app>; und
                        auf welichen <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag du kümst
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dein scheimbot mit
                                <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt und das an uns vorderst, so
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir dir <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheimbot<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        vollen gewalt von <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>obgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> Hansen Veyrabent,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, hie vor des reiches
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> czü <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czoge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>slewnige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> helffen; und dar czü solt du unser sicher
                        geleitt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czü uns, bey uns und
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> uns
                                <expan>ungeu<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>qu<ex>in</ex>ta</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>purific<ex>acionis</ex></expan> Marie. <app>
<note place="bottomcentral">Den brief hat man ir
                                    <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> czü
                                <expan>Eyst<ex>et</ex></expan> <app><note><q type="date">am samstag vor
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen tag</q>31.01.1411</note></app>, da bey was
                                        <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Dickerman und
                                        <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>meist<ex>er</ex>.</expan>
</note>
</app></ab></div>
</div></body>
